          discovered</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          </msItem>
                          <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.7">
                            <locus from="118v"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1928Mashaf">Maṣḥafa fǝlsatā la-Māryām</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          </msItem>
                          <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.8">
                            <locus from="133v"/>
                            <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1750LahaMa">ላሀ፡ ማርያም፡</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          </msItem>
                          <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.9">
                            <locus from="149r"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6180HomilyChurches">Homily on the construction of churches dedicated to
          Mary for the day of her feast on 21st of Sane</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          </msItem>
                          <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.10">
                            <locus from="150r"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6178BasilPhilippi">Baʾǝnta ḥǝnḍā beta krǝstiyān la-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝna nǝṣǝḥt
          Māryām ba-ʿǝlata qǝddāse ʾama 20wa1 la-Sane ba-salāma ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          </msItem>
                          <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.11">
                            <locus from="158r"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3082RepCh362">Malkǝʾa kidāna mǝḥrat</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                              እግዚአብሔር፡ ወሃቤ፡ ብርሃን፡ ዘይሤለስ፡ በአካሉ።
                            </incipit>
                          </msItem>
                          <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.12">
                            <locus from="162r"/>
                            <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2487Vision">
                            ዘይትነበብ፡ በበዓለ፡ ቍስቋም፡</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          </msItem>
                          <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.13">
                            <locus from="177v"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1643Homily">Dǝrsān manāzǝz wa-fǝśśǝḥa baʾǝnta zenā qǝddāse beta krǝstiyān
          za-tǝʾǝmǝrt</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          </msItem>
                          <note><ref target="#ms_i1.12"/> and <ref target="#ms_i2.13"/>
                        are divided so as to form in connection a complete course of readings for the 12
                      months.</note>
                        </msItem>
